# pipe & flow Quick Reference

## pipe - Transform a Value

```typescript
import { pipe } from 'fp-ts/function'

// pipe(startValue, fn1, fn2, fn3)
// = fn3(fn2(fn1(startValue)))

const result = pipe(
  '  hello world  ',
  s => s.trim(),
  s => s.toUpperCase(),
  s => s.split(' ')
)
// ['HELLO', 'WORLD']
```

